# RSYNC

## Installation

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install rsync -y
```

## Sauvegarde locale

```bash
rsync -av /source/ /destination/
```

Exemple :

```bash
rsync -av /home/Travail/ /tmp/Travail/
```

## Sauvegarde distante SSH

```bash
rsync -e ssh -avz /source/ user@IP:/destination/
```

Exemple :

```bash
rsync -e ssh -avz /home/Travail/ geoff@192.168.100.20:/tmp/Travail/
```

## Vérification

```bash
ls /tmp/Travail
```

## Connexion SSH

```bash
ssh geoff@192.168.100.20
```

